We are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we handle and protect your personal information while you play Hangman.

1. Data Collection

We collect minimal data.
The game hangman receives and stores no personal information.
The only information collected and stored is the state of the hangman game.
This consists of the word to guess, the length of the word, the number
of guesses, and the sequence of guesses.

2. Use of Data

Collected data is solely used to support the game play of hangman.

3. Data Sharing

We do not share your data with any third parties.

4. Changes to the privacy policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do,
we will post an updated version on this page, unless another type of
notice is required by applicable law.
